南非在歷史上一直吸收了大量荷蘭語移民<ref name="auto2">{{harvp|Deumert|2004}}</ref>，由於長期與位於歐洲本土的荷蘭語社群隔離，當地的荷蘭語逐漸演變成爲今天的南非荷蘭語。<ref name="coetzee">{{Cite book|url=http://www.dbnl.org/arch/coet003stan01_01/pag/coet003stan01_01.pdf|title=Standaard-Afrikaans|last=Coetzee|first=Abel|publisher=Pers van die Universiteit van die Witwatersrand|year=1948|access-date=September 17, 2014|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702150541/https://www.dbnl.org/arch/coet003stan01_01/pag/coet003stan01_01.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

直到1920年代，歐洲荷蘭語一直是南非的標準書面語。後來由於南非興起的民族主義運動，標準書面語遂改爲南非荷蘭語。1925年，南非通過憲法修正案，將[[南非聯邦|南非聯盟]]1905年憲法中的第137條改爲“本法所指的荷蘭語，於此將其重定義爲南非荷蘭語。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=South Africa: Legislation: 1910–2015|url=http://www.archontology.org/nations/south_africa/01_laws.php|website=Archontology.org|access-date=August 12, 2015|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709103320/http://www.archontology.org/nations/south_africa/01_laws.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite speech|last=Mpati|first=Lex|author-link=Lex Mpati|event=Inaugural Lecture|location=University of the Free State|date=6 October 2004|title=Transformation in the Judiciary – A Constitutional Imperative|url=http://www.supremecourtofappeal.gov.za/speeches/mpati.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070816125902/http://www.supremecourtofappeal.gov.za/speeches/mpati.pdf|archive-date=August 16, 2007}}</ref>1983年憲法則僅列英語和南非荷蘭語爲官方語言。南非荷蘭語中90-95%的詞彙來自荷蘭語<ref>{{harvp|Mesthrie|1995|p=214}}</ref><ref>{{harvp|Brachin|Vincent|1985|p=132}}</ref>。兩種語言能夠[[相互理解性|互通]]，荷蘭語人士比南非荷蘭語人士更能明白對方<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mutual Comprehensibility of Written Afrikaans and Dutch: Symmetrical or Asymmetrical?|url=http://llc.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/21/4/543|first1=C.|last2=van Bezooijen|first2=R.|date=2006|journal=Literary and Linguistic Computing|issue=4|doi=10.1093/llc/fql036|volume=21|pages=543–557|last1=Gooskens|access-date=August 19, 2012|archive-date=2008-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212002827/http://llc.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/21/4/543|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

南非荷蘭語是[[南非|南非]]第三多人使用的語言（13.5%）<ref name="Key results of the 2011 census">[http://www.statssa.gov.za/Census2011/Products/Census_2011_Key_results.pdf Key results of the 2011 census]{{dead link|date=December 2016|bot=InternetArchiveBot|fix-attempted=yes}}, Statistics South Africa</ref>，其中53%爲有色人，42.4%爲白人<ref>{{cite web|title=Primary tables: Census '96 and 2001 compared|url=http://www.statssa.gov.za/census01/html/RSAPrimary.pdf|publisher=Statistics South Africa|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061130140908/http://www.statssa.gov.za/census01/html/RSAPrimary.pdf|archive-date=November 30, 2006}}</ref>。1996年，40%的南非人稱自己擁有至少基本的南非荷蘭語水平<ref>{{harvp|Webb|2003}}</ref>。南非荷蘭語是[[纳米比亚|納米比亞]]的[[通用語|通用語]]<ref name="auto22">{{harvp|Deumert|2004}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Namibia|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/wa.html#People|work=The World Factbook|publisher=CIA|access-date=August 19, 2012|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830150855/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/wa.html#People|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{harvp|Adegbija|1994|p=26}}</ref>，爲11%人口的母語<ref>{{Cite web|title=About Namibia|url=http://www.grnnet.gov.na/aboutnam.html|date=2007|website=Government of the Republic of Namibia|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206042235/http://www.grnnet.gov.na/aboutnam.html|archive-date=December 6, 2008}}</ref>。南非荷蘭語是非洲南部710萬人的母語<ref name="Key results of the 2011 census2">[http://www.statssa.gov.za/Census2011/Products/Census_2011_Key_results.pdf Key results of the 2011 census]{{dead link|date=December 2016|bot=InternetArchiveBot|fix-attempted=yes}}, Statistics South Africa</ref>，同時該語亦是全球另外至少1000萬人的第二語言<ref>{{Cite web|title=Afrikaans|url=http://www.ethnologue.com/show_language.asp?code=afr|website=Ethnologue|access-date=August 19, 2012|archive-date=2010-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304114859/http://www.ethnologue.com/show_language.asp?code=afr|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與之相對，標準荷蘭語則有2300萬母語人士<ref name="taalgebied2">{{Cite web|title=Het Nederlandse taalgebied|url=http://taalunieversum.org/taalpeil/2005/het_nederlandse_taalgebied.html|date=2005|language=nl|website=taalunieversum.org|trans-title=The Dutch language area|access-date=November 4, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081023045519/http://taalunieversum.org/taalpeil/2005/het_nederlandse_taalgebied.html|archive-date=2008-10-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>及500萬第二語言人士<ref name="Eurobarometer Languages">{{cite web|title=Special Eurobarometer 243: Europeans and their Languages (Survey)|url=http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_243_en.pdf|accessdate=February 3, 2007|author=[[European_Commission|European Commission]]|year=2006|publisher=[[Europa_(web_portal)|Europa]]|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414102658/http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_243_en.pdf|dead-url=no}} "1% of the EU population claims to speak Dutch well enough in order to have a conversation." (page 153).</ref>。

歷史上，[[荷屬黃金海岸|荷屬黃金海岸]]（今屬[[加纳|加納]]）曾是荷蘭的殖民地，但是今天已經完全被英語同化。雖然[[比屬剛果|比屬剛果]]和[[盧安達-烏隆地|盧旺達-烏隆迪]]歷史上曾爲比利時的殖民地，但是由於殖民地當局使用法語，因此荷蘭語在本地幾乎沒有留下任何影響。<ref>[http://archives.lesoir.be/-pasopo-disent-les-ketjes-de-lubumbashi_t-19990928-Z0H9ZJ.html «Pasopo» disent les «ketjes» de Lubumbashi] {{Wayback|url=http://archives.lesoir.be/-pasopo-disent-les-ketjes-de-lubumbashi_t-19990928-Z0H9ZJ.html |date=20161018010230 }} – [[Le_Soir|Le Soir]], September 28, 1999</ref>

